  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Glagoli vremena je važno raspravljati o tome kada se nešto dogodi.</p>\n<p>Funkcija <span class=\"highlighted-text\">in</span> se koristi za mesece, godine, vekove i duge periode. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">We will update the software in July</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I started learning coding in 2022</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I like to work in the morning</span>.</p>\n<p>Polje <span class=\"highlighted-text\">on</span> se koristi za dane i datume. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Our team meets on Mondays</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">The coding class is on April 10th</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I finished the task on the last day</span>.</p>\n<p>Glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">at</span> se koristi za određivanje stvarnih vremena dana. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Our meeting is at 9 AM</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I begin coding at 10 AM</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">We have lunch at 12 PM</span>.</p>\n</section>",
